He sees Dr. Stringer
and his therapist

00:10:03.402 --> 00:10:06.305 line:71%
every four to six weeks
for booster sessions.

00:10:06.405 --> 00:10:09.342 line:71%
He's also learning to accept
that he will always grapple

00:10:09.442 --> 00:10:11.444 line:71%
with cognitive
challenges.

