<i> Did you know that the
 natural vibrations of cars</i>

00:10:19.552 --> 00:10:21.053 line:71%
can make people sleepy?

00:10:21.153 --> 00:10:23.189 line:71%
Even if they're well
rested and healthy.

00:10:23.289 --> 00:10:24.924 line:71%
This is a big problem,

00:10:25.024 --> 00:10:26.258 line:71%
when you consider
how much time

00:10:26.359 --> 00:10:28.327 line:71%
we spend in our cars
these days.

00:10:28.427 --> 00:10:30.896 line:71%
