 20% of fatal crashes</i>

00:10:30.997 --> 00:10:32.732 line:71%
<i> involve driver fatigue.</i>

00:10:32.832 --> 00:10:34.333 line:71%
<i> In a study out
 of Australia,</i>

00:10:34.433 --> 00:10:36.202 line:71%
<i> volunteers were
 tested in simulators</i>

00:10:36.302 --> 00:10:38.270 line:71%
<i> that mimicked driving
 on the highway.</i>

00:10:38.371 --> 00:10:40.573 line:71%
