 at the 60 minute mark.</i>

00:10:46.178 --> 00:10:47.647 line:71%
The research is ongoing.

00:10:47.747 --> 00:10:50.216 line:71%
But the hope is that
future carseat designs

00:10:50.316 --> 00:10:51.717 line:71%
could include
something to fight

00:10:51.817 --> 00:10:54.253 line:71%
this vibration-induced
sleepiness.

