We know people can be
addicted to many things.

00:11:04.397 --> 00:11:07.767 line:71%
From food, to alcohol,
to drugs.

00:11:07.867 --> 00:11:11.237 line:71%
Now add video games
to the list.

00:11:11.337 --> 00:11:14.173 line:71%
The World Health Organization
has named Gaming Disorder

00:11:14.273 --> 00:11:15.675 line:71%
as a mental health
condition

00:11:15.775 --> 00:11:18.944 line:71%
in its International
Classification of Diseases.

00:11:19.045 --> 00:11:21.113 line:71%
We take a look at
Gaming Disorder.

00:11:21.213 --> 00:11:25.718 line:71%
What it means to video gamers
and their brains.

00:11:25.818 --> 00:11:28.888 line:64%
<i> It looks like a Christmas
 morning race down the stairs.</i>

00:11:28.988 --> 00:11:30.990 line:64%
<i> But instead of presents
 beneath the tree</i>

00:11:31.090 --> 00:11:33.759 line:64%
<i> for the Watt Brothers,
 there is this.</i>

00:11:36.696 --> 00:11:39.432 line:71%
<i> That race is because
 whoever gets there first...</i>

00:11:39.532 --> 00:11:40.499 line:71%
Rock, paper,
scissors, shoot.

00:11:40.599 --> 00:11:41.367 line:71%
<i> ... plays first.</i>

00:11:41.467 --> 00:11:42.468 line:71%
Rock, paper,
scissors, shoot.

