And then it comes down
to one person who wins.

00:11:50.176 --> 00:11:53.779 line:68%
<i> (Jaye)
 "Fortnite" is a far cry from
 your father's video games.</i>

00:11:53.879 --> 00:11:55.214 line:71%
I get irritated a lot.

