<i> (Jaye)
 My son, Jude, is 13.</i>

00:14:45.117 --> 00:14:46.418 line:71%
<i> Very 13.</i>

00:14:46.518 --> 00:14:48.053 line:71%
<i> We limit his
 playing time.</i>

