<i> Not a popular decision.</i>

00:14:49.588 --> 00:14:51.090 line:71%
<i> You don't think that
 we should limit</i>

00:14:51.190 --> 00:14:52.591 line:57%
<i> your video game
 playing time?</i>

00:14:52.691 --> 00:14:53.559 line:71%
No, no, no, no.

00:14:53.659 --> 00:14:54.760 line:71%
You should
totally limit it.

