My port of fort now.

00:15:00.232 --> 00:15:02.334 line:71%
<i> My friends, their parents
 don't even care.</i>

00:15:02.434 --> 00:15:04.403 line:71%
<i> Like, one of my friends
 are on six hours a day.</i>

00:15:04.503 --> 00:15:06.572 line:68%
<i> (Jaye)
 I can't fact check
 that last statement,</i>

00:15:06.672 --> 00:15:08.073 line:71%
<i> but I do think
 it's interesting</i>

00:15:08.173 --> 00:15:11.577 line:71%
<i>when Jude explains how he feels
after playing for a long time.</i>

00:15:11.677 --> 00:15:15.080 line:71%
<i> I get, actually,
 very bored and mad,</i>

00:15:15.180 --> 00:15:18.684 line:71%
and my head gets angry,
