<i> (Dr. Welsh)
 What are the screen habits?</i>

00:15:36.468 --> 00:15:39.705 line:71%
<i> How much time is the child
 or adolescent spending?</i>

00:15:39.805 --> 00:15:41.674 line:71%
<i> And what are
 they playing?</i>

00:15:41.774 --> 00:15:44.944 line:71%
<i> And what really happens
 when you set limits?</i>

00:15:45.044 --> 00:15:48.213 line:68%
<i> (Jaye)
 My son will argue our limits
 are killing his social life.</i>

00:15:48.314 --> 00:15:49.982 line:71%
<i> He meets up with
 his friends online.</i>

00:15:50.082 --> 00:15:51.617 line:71%
<i> So do the Watt Brothers,</i>

00:15:51.717 --> 00:15:55.154 line:71%
<i>and millions of adolescent and
adult gamers across the country</i>

