There's strategy
around it.

00:16:11.337 --> 00:16:13.105 line:71%
There's, you know,
critical thinking,

00:16:13.205 --> 00:16:15.507 line:71%
and things like that,
that I like about it.

00:16:15.607 --> 00:16:17.576 line:57%
It's a very
new diagnosis.

00:16:17.676 --> 00:16:20.379 line:57%
We still have a lot
to learn about it.

00:16:20.479 --> 00:16:22.348 line:57%
<i> (Jaye)
 More research is underway.</i>

00:16:22.448 --> 00:16:25.918 line:71%
<i> And long-term impacts of
 too much gaming are not known.</i>

00:16:26.018 --> 00:16:28.821 line:71%
<i> Treatment is Cognitive
 Behavioral Therapy.</i>

00:16:28.921 --> 00:16:30.422 line:71%
<i> A talk therapy
 that helps people</i>

00:16:30.522 --> 00:16:33.492 line:71%
<i> adopt healthier
 behaviors and thoughts.</i>

00:16:33.592 --> 00:16:35.694 line:71%
<i> The battle for
 balance will rage on</i>

00:16:35.794 --> 00:16:37.529 line:71%
<i> in homes across America,</i>

00:16:37.629 --> 00:16:40.499 line:71%
<i> with some parents still
 clinging to the hope</i>

00:16:40.599 --> 00:16:44.336 line:71%
<i> that video games
 do not reign supreme.</i>

00:16:44.436 --> 00:16:45.938 line:71%
I think you'll have--

00:16:46.038 --> 00:16:47.439 line:57%
at least one of 'em
will say that

00:16:47.539 --> 00:16:49.308 line:57%
there's other things
they prefer to do,

00:16:49.408 --> 00:16:50.943 line:64%
than video games.

00:16:51.043 --> 00:16:52.478 line:57%
And I would call
that denial.

00:16:52.578 --> 00:16:54.613 line:64%
<i> (laughter)</i>

00:16:57.483 --> 00:16:59.918 line:71%
Some mental health experts
say addiction to gaming

00:17:00.019 --> 00:17:02.287 line:71%
can be a symptom of
an underlying condition,

00:17:02.388 --> 00:17:04.456 line:71%
like depression,
or ADHD.

00:17:04.556 --> 00:17:05.858 line:71%
And that just
because a kid

00:17:05.958 --> 00:17:07.893 line:71%
spends hours
playing video games

00:17:07.993 --> 00:17:09.995 line:71%
doesn't mean
they're an addict.

00:17:10.095 --> 00:17:13.165 line:71%
That's why Gaming Disorder
can only be diagnosed

00:17:13.265 --> 00:17:15.267 line:71%
by a mental health
professional.

